<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title></title>
  </head>
  <body>

    <h1>You're all set!</h1>
    <br>
    <h3>Bookings details:</h3>
    <br>
    <table class="table mt-5">
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Your car</td>
          <td><%= "#{@booking.car.make} #{@booking.car.model}" %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Owner</td>
          <td><%= @booking.car.user.firstname %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Pick up date</td>
          <td><%= @booking.date_from%></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Return date</td>
          <td><%= @booking.date_to %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Price per day</td>
          <td><%= number_to_currency(@booking.price_per_day) %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-top: solid grey 2px;">
          <td class="d-flex justify-content-end pr-5">
            <strong>Sub-total</strong>
          </td>
          <% ppd = @booking.price_per_day %>
          <% days = (@booking.date_to - @booking.date_from).to_i %>
          <td><strong><%= number_to_currency(ppd * days) %></strong><span class="text-success"> PAID</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Price per km</td>
          <td><%= number_to_currency(@booking.price_per_km) %></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <br>
    <p>We'll email you a receipt for the final payment after your trip, pending kilometers travelled.</p>
    <p>You can contact the owner via the application in 'My trip'</p>
    <p>Link to website: https://rentmycar.herokuapp.com/</p>
    <br>
    <p>Enjoy your adventure!</p>
    <br>
    <br>
    <p>Kind regards,</p>
    <p>The Rent-my-cat development team</p>

  </body>
</html>
